4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to equip individuals with the foundational and practical skills needed to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 participants. No prior experience is necessary, and students can select to learn in either English or Spanish. Key topics cover Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official completion certificate. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop